    {
      "id": "detailed_1_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_1",
      "description": "This vehicle is in absolute mint condition, truly a showroom-quality find. The exterior paint is flawless with a deep, mirror-like shine, and the interior remains in pristine, factory-fresh state with no signs of wear. Mechanically, it performs perfectly, having been meticulously maintained and stored in a climate-controlled environment. This is a rare opportunity to own a vehicle that looks and drives as if it just rolled off the assembly line.",
